title: GOP lawmaker hears demands for 'a fighter' for speaker
text: > Texas GOP lawmaker hears demands for 'a fighter' for speaker Rep. Blake Farenthold, R-Texas, holds a town hall meeting Thursday, Oct. 15, 2015, in Wharton, Texas. Farenthold is reckoning with demands from voters that may be difficult, even impossible, to satisfy. Voters see a chance to restore conservative leadership to the House and finally take the fight to Obama. Yet even though itâ€™s not yet clear who will replace House Speaker John Boehner, the budgetary deadlines looming in coming months raise the possibility that the next speaker could be forced into the same compromises and retreats as the current one. (AP Photo/Pat Sullivan)
